high_descs: Go to the sink
Pick up the knife from the sink
Take the knife to the cabinet with marble top
Slice the potato on the cabinet top
Carry the knife back to the sink
Put the knife into the sink
Go back to the cabinet with the cut potato
Pick up a slice of potato
Go to the stove and raise the potato slice
Put the potato slice inside the microwave above the stove and take it out after heating
Take the potato slice to the sink
Place the potato slice in the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato slice in a sink

high_descs: Move forward and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife inside the sink.
Turn left and head towards the cabinet on your left.
Slice the potato on the cabinet.
Turn right across the room and head towards the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn left and head towards the sink on your right.
Pick a sliced of potato from the cabinet.
Turn right and move to the microwave on your left.
Open the microwave and put the sliced potato in it and close it, then pick up the sliced potato from the microwave.
Turn right across the room and face the sink on your left.
Put the sliced potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot sliced potato in sink.
